datasets.name: 749e0114
queryLines:
with 
dedicated_tables as (select * from IDENTIFIER('`PROFILER_CATALOG`.`PROFILER_SCHEMA`.dedicated_tables')),
dedicated_views as (select * from IDENTIFIER('`PROFILER_CATALOG`.`PROFILER_SCHEMA`.dedicated_views')),

tables as (
  select table_catalog, table_schema, table_name
  from dedicated_tables
  where table_type != 'VIEW'
  qualify row_number() over (partition by table_catalog, table_schema, table_name order by table_name) =1

),
table_counts as (
  select 
    table_catalog as catalog,
    table_schema as schema,
    'Tables' as object_type,
    count(*) as num_objects
  from tables
  group by 1, 2 order by 3 desc
  limit 10
),

views as (
  select table_catalog, table_schema, table_name
  from dedicated_views
  qualify row_number() over (partition by table_catalog, table_schema, table_name order by table_name) =1

),
view_counts as (
  select 
    table_catalog as catalog,
    table_schema as schema,
    'Views' as object_type,
    count(*) as num_objects
  from views
  group by 1, 2 order by 3 desc
  limit 10
)



select 
  *
from 
(
  select * from table_counts
  union all
  select * from view_counts
) X
order by 3 desc

datasets.name: 3d2f9598
queryLines:
with 
dedicated_session_requests as (
  select * from IDENTIFIER('`PROFILER_CATALOG`.`PROFILER_SCHEMA`.dedicated_session_requests')
  qualify row_number() OVER ( partition by pool_name, session_id, request_id order by end_time) = 1
  ),
commands as (
  select 
    pool_name, 
    session_id, 
    request_id, 
    command,
    from_utc_timestamp(start_time, 'US/Eastern') start_time,
    from_utc_timestamp(end_time, 'US/Eastern') end_time,
    command_w1,
    command_w2,
    command_type,
    CASE
      WHEN command_type in ('DML', 'ROUTINE', 'DDL') THEN 'ETL'
      WHEN command_type = 'QUERY' THEN 'SQL Serving'
      ELSE 'OTHER'
    END as workload_type
  from dedicated_session_requests
  where 
    start_time is not null and end_time is not null
    AND command_w1 not in ('SET', 'USE') 
    AND not (command_w1 = 'SELECT' and command_w2 = '@@SPID;')
    AND not (command_w1 = 'EXEC' and command_w2 = '[SP_EXECUTESQL]')  
),
timex_10min_windows as (
  select
    make_timestamp(year(dt), month(dt), day(dt), t_hours.hr, t_minutes.min*10, 00) as st,
    make_timestamp(year(dt), month(dt), day(dt), t_hours.hr, (t_minutes.min+1)*10-1, 59.999) as ed
  from
    (
      select distinct date(start_time) dt from commands 
      union
      select distinct date(end_time) dt from commands
    ) x,
  (
    select explode(sequence(0, 23)) hr
  ) t_hours,
  (
    select explode(sequence(0, 5)) min 
  ) t_minutes  
),
daily_10min_interval_metrics as (
    select
      date_format(st, "HH:mm") as st,
      workload_type,
      command_type,
      avg(query_count) avg_query_count,
      min(query_count) min_query_count,
      max(query_count) max_query_count
    from (  
      select
        st,
        ed,
        workload_type,
        command_type,
        count(distinct request_id) as query_count
      from timex_10min_windows X
      left join commands  Y
      on (start_time between X.st and X.ed) or (end_time between X.st and X.ed) 
      group by 1, 2, 3, 4
    )
    group by 1, 2, 3
    order by 1, 2, 3
  )


select
 *,
 sum(avg_query_count) over (partition by st, workload_type)/10 as queries_per_minute_by_workload
from  daily_10min_interval_metrics

datasets.name: 5d0d81e1
queryLines:
with 
sessions as (
  select * from IDENTIFIER('`PROFILER_CATALOG`.`PROFILER_SCHEMA`.dedicated_sessions')
  qualify row_number() over (partition by pool_name, session_id order by query_count desc ) = 1 
  ),
 app_session_queries as (
  select 
    pool_name, 
    query_count,
    login_time,
    login_user_type,    
    case 
      WHEN trim(lower(regexp_extract(app_name, '^(\\w+\\s+\\w+)-(\\w+)-(\\w+)-(\\w+)', 1 ))) = 'data integration' THEN 'Azure Data Integration Pipeline'
        WHEN trim(lower(regexp_extract(app_name, '^(\\w+)_(\\w+)', 1 ))) = 'azurestreamanalytics' THEN 'Azure Stream Analytics'
        WHEN trim(lower(regexp_extract(app_name, '^(\\w+)\\s*(\\d+)', 1 ))) = 'tableau' THEN 'Tableau'
      WHEN instr(app_name, 'SQL Server Management Studio') > 0 THEN 'Microsoft SSMS'
      ELSE app_name
    END as app_name_condt
  from sessions
)

select
  pool_name,
  app_name_condt as app_name,
  sum(query_count)
from app_session_queries
where login_user_type <> 'USER'
group by 1, 2 order by 3 desc

datasets.name: b4a08f84

queryLines:
with 
sessions as (
  select * from IDENTIFIER('`PROFILER_CATALOG`.`PROFILER_SCHEMA`.dedicated_sessions')
  qualify row_number() over (partition by pool_name, session_id order by query_count desc ) = 1 
  ),
sessions_silver as (
  select 
    pool_name, 
    query_count,
    login_time,
    login_user,
    login_user_type,    
    case
      WHEN trim(app_name) = '' or app_name is null THEN 'UNKOWN'
      WHEN trim(lower(regexp_extract(app_name, '^(\\w+\\s+\\w+)-(\\w+)-(\\w+)-(\\w+)', 1 ))) = 'data integration' THEN 'Azure Data Integration Pipeline'
      WHEN trim(lower(regexp_extract(app_name, '^(\\w+)_(\\w+)', 1 ))) = 'azurestreamanalytics' THEN 'Azure Stream Analytics'
      WHEN trim(lower(regexp_extract(app_name, '^(\\w+)\\s*(\\d+)', 1 ))) = 'tableau' THEN 'Tableau'
      WHEN instr(app_name, 'SQL Server Management Studio') > 0 THEN 'Microsoft SSMS'
      ELSE app_name
    END as app_name_condt
  from sessions
),
user_app_sessions as (
    select
      pool_name as stage1,
      case when login_user_type = 'USER' THEN 'USER_SESSION' ELSE app_name_condt END stage2,
      login_user as stage3,
      query_count as value
    from sessions_silver
),
session_activity_sankey as (
  select stage1, stage2, stage3 , sum(value) as value from user_app_sessions group by 1, 2, 3
)
select
  stage1,
  stage2,
  CASE 
    WHEN dense_rank() over (partition by stage2 order by value desc) <= :`topN` THEN stage3 
    WHEN stage2 = 'USER_SESSION' THEN 'other.user'
    ELSE 'other.app'
  END stage3,
  value
from 
  session_activity_sankey

datasets.name: e18e029d
queryLines:
with 
dedicated_session_requests as (
  select * from IDENTIFIER('`PROFILER_CATALOG`.`PROFILER_SCHEMA`.dedicated_session_requests')
  qualify row_number() OVER ( partition by pool_name, session_id, request_id order by end_time) = 1
  ),
dedicated_sessions as (
  select * from IDENTIFIER('`PROFILER_CATALOG`.`PROFILER_SCHEMA`.dedicated_sessions')
  qualify row_number() over (partition by pool_name, session_id order by query_count desc ) = 1 
  ),
session_requests_silver as (
  select 
    pool_name, 
    session_id, 
    request_id, 
    command,
    start_time,
    end_time,
    (unix_millis(from_utc_timestamp(end_time, 'US/Eastern')) - unix_millis(from_utc_timestamp(start_time, 'US/Eastern'))) as exec_wall_misecs,    
    command_w1,
    command_w2,
    command_type,
    CASE
      WHEN command_type in ('DML', 'ROUTINE', 'DDL') THEN 'ETL'
      WHEN command_type = 'QUERY' THEN 'SQL Serving'
      ELSE 'OTHER'
    END as workload_type
  from dedicated_session_requests
  where 
  command_w1 not in ('SET', 'USE') AND 
  not (command_w1 = 'SELECT' and command_w2 = '@@SPID;') AND 
  not (command_w1 = 'EXEC' and command_w2 = '[SP_EXECUTESQL]')    
),
sessions_silver as (
  select 
    pool_name, 
    query_count,
    login_time,
    session_id,
    login_user || "." || dense_rank() over (partition by login_user order by login_user_sha2) as login_user,
    login_user_type,    
    CASE
      WHEN login_user_type = 'USER' THEN 'USER_SESSION'
        WHEN trim(app_name) = '' or app_name is null THEN 'UNKOWN'
        WHEN trim(lower(regexp_extract(app_name, '^(\\w+\\s+\\w+)-(\\w+)-(\\w+)-(\\w+)', 1 ))) = 'data integration' THEN 'Azure Data Integration Pipeline'
        WHEN trim(lower(regexp_extract(app_name, '^(\\w+)_(\\w+)', 1 ))) = 'azurestreamanalytics' THEN 'Azure Stream Analytics'
        WHEN trim(lower(regexp_extract(app_name, '^(\\w+)\\s*(\\d+)', 1 ))) = 'tableau' THEN 'Tableau'
        WHEN instr(app_name, 'SQL Server Management Studio') > 0 THEN 'Microsoft SSMS'
        ELSE app_name
    END as app_name
  from dedicated_sessions
),
app_and_user_session_sankey as (
select 
  pool_name as stage1,
  app_name as stage2,
  login_user as stage3,
  command_type as stage4,
  workload_type as stage5,
  sum(exec_wall_misecs) as value
from sessions_silver
join session_requests_silver
using (pool_name, session_id)
group by 1, 2, 3, 4, 5
)
select 
  stage1,
  stage2,
  
  CASE 
    WHEN dense_rank() over (partition by stage4, stage5 order by value desc) <= :`topN` THEN stage3 
    WHEN stage2 = 'USER_SESSION' THEN 'other.user'
    ELSE 'other.app'
  END stage3,
  stage4,
  stage5,
  value
from 
  app_and_user_session_sankey

datasets.name: 4d870a15
queryLines:
with 
dedicated_session_requests as (select * from IDENTIFIER('`PROFILER_CATALOG`.`PROFILER_SCHEMA`.dedicated_session_requests')),
commands as (
  select 
    pool_name, 
    session_id, 
    request_id, 
    command,
    start_time,
    end_time,
    (unix_millis(from_utc_timestamp(end_time, 'US/Eastern')) - unix_millis(from_utc_timestamp(start_time, 'US/Eastern'))) as exec_wall_misecs,    
    
    command_w1,
    command_w2,
    command_type
  from dedicated_session_requests
  qualify row_number() OVER ( partition by pool_name, session_id, request_id order by end_time) = 1
),
data_commands as (
  select * from commands 
  where 
  command_w1 not in ('SET', 'USE') 
  AND not (command_w1 = 'SELECT' and command_w2 = '@@SPID;')
  AND not (command_w1 = 'EXEC' and command_w2 = '[SP_EXECUTESQL]')
),
typed_commands as (
  select
    
    *
  from data_commands
),
typed_commands_by_volume as (
  select command_type, 'Volume' as metric_type, count(*)  as value 
  from typed_commands
  group by 1, 2 
  order by 3 desc
),
typed_commands_by_time as (
  select command_type, 'Time (Wall)' as metric_type, sum(exec_wall_misecs)/1000  as value 
  from typed_commands
  group by 1, 2 
  order by 3 desc
)
select * from typed_commands_by_volume
union all
select * from typed_commands_by_time
